<HEADLINE> Mighty Ducks Sign Defenseman </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ANAHEIM, Calif. (AP) -- Defenseman Jason Marshall has signed a  
two-year contract with the Anaheim Mighty Ducks, the team announced 
Tuesday. 
</P>
