<HEADLINE> McRae Added to Blue Jays Roster </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	MINNEAPOLIS (AP) -- The Toronto Blue Jays placed first baseman  
David Segui on the 15-day disabled list Tuesday to make room for 
Brian McRae. 
